  "body": "## What?\r\nProposal for enhancements to the \"send entire balance\" UI.\r\n\r\n#### MyCrypto Current \r\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-21 at 2 23 13 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7861465/37732565-673cea06-2d13-11e8-8f69-9b4a819615c8.png\">\r\n\r\nInstead of \"Send Entire Balance\" shown below the amount field, a more common UI is including an element on the far right of the input (as shown below). \r\n\r\n#### Trezor\r\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-21 at 2 16 34 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7861465/37732252-7d48b902-2d12-11e8-8aad-94a521cdb019.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Mockup\r\n<img width=\"629\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-21 at 2 25 49 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7861465/37732678-c6cc20cc-2d13-11e8-8a17-f23a0f150bb7.png\">\r\n\r\n- [ ] Enhance the send entire balance UI by providing a clickable element show within the input field.\r\n",
